metadata.name: UNTOUCHED
metadata.description:
\>The secret code is entered and a small door swings open.

\>Inside is an old box weathered beyond recognition.

\>How long has it been here? A month? A decade? A century?

\>The box creakily opens.

\>Inside is a pristine, untouched manilla folder.

\>To the naked eye it looks ordinary. But the tingling on the back of your neck says thereâ€™s something more.

\>You pick it up. Instantly your mind is flooded with images, ideas, stories, visions you can only begin to discern.

\>You look at the folder in your hands with wonder. Inside you a pulsing energy you can only describe as "inspiration" grows.
